msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Ha u le ntle ho US, re kgothaletsa NOWPayments (mafa a lekakha, ho tsamaisa "
"ho morero oa hau). Ha u le ho US, Stripe Crypto hape ke khetho. U ka thusa "
"litšebeletso tse ngata le ho lefa ba liatlehang ba hau ho khetha!"

