"Stripe Crypto payments (USDC) are ONLY available for US-based businesses. If"
" you are outside the US, Stripe will only accept credit card payments to "
"your Stripe balance (not directly to crypto)."
msgstr ""
"Litšenyehelo tsa Stripe Crypto (USDC) li thuse feela lipapali tsa US. Haeba "
"u se ka US, Stripe e tla amohela feela litšenyehelo tsa kariti ho balansi ea"
" Stripe ea hau (ha ho tswela pele ho crypto)."

msgid ""
"If you are in the US, you can use Stripe to receive crypto directly. If "
"outside, consider NOWPayments or CoinGate for direct crypto payouts."
msgstr ""
"Haeba u le US, u ka sebelisa Stripe ho fumana crypto ka potlako. Haeba u se "
"ka US, itokisetsa NOWPayments kapa CoinGate bakeng sa ditshupetso tsa crypto"
" tsa potlako."

