msgid "Let My Girl Friend Enjoy Our Coffee"
msgstr "Bolehe Khabana ya ka ho leahla ka khofi ea rona"

msgid ""
"A powerful, free donation and payment widget that allows your visitors to "
"support you via credit card or cryptocurrency (Quai). No monthly fees, no "
"third-party subscriptions – just your wallet and free services."
msgstr ""
"Sesebelisoa sa litšenyehelo le litšenyehelo tsa thupa e matla, ea "
"phatlalatsa le e sebetsang ka ho sebaka se se le se se sa lokelang, se u "
"lumellang boitsebiso ba hao ho u tšehetsa ka karatla kapa crypto (Quai). Ha "
"ho na litšenyehelo tsa mahala, ha ho na likhatiso tsa thahasello le batho ba"
" bonngoe – feela wallet ya hao le litšebeletso tsa mahala."

msgid ""
"Some browsers block third-party scripts for privacy. This proxy loads "
"scripts through your own server to bypass these blocks."
msgstr ""
"Bohlokoa ba li-browsers bo se li bontša li-script tsa ba bangwe ho ba "
"lephata. Proxy ena e kenya li-script ka tsela ya seva ea hao ho felisa "
"litšenyehelo tsena."

msgid ""
"You can update the script URLs below if the original URLs change or if you "
"want to use a different CDN."
msgstr ""
"O ka ntlafatsa URLs tsa script ho tlase haeba URLs tsa tlhahiso li fetoloa "
"kapa haeba o batle ho sebelisa CDN e fapaneng."

